ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Learning initial statistical analysis tests and SAS. Useful to know for our research, and even to critically read research reports.

Yes, I will. this course is essential for our future when we conduct our own researches, as it provided basic skills that can help us choose statistic methods right for our research needs and know how to manage our research data and know when to seek help withstatistic consultation.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It helped refresh statistics and gave a more in-depth look at statistical tests. This was an intro to SAS for me, which is complex. I'm sure this will be useful for my research.

Like what I said above, it provided basic skills that can help us choose statistic methods right for our research needs and know how to manage our research data and know when to seek help with statistic consultation. those knowledge and skills are crucial for the success of a study.
